videos.headline: Boise State QB throws 67-yard missile for TD
videos.description: Boise State QB Brett Rypien throws a 67-yard rocket to WR John Hightower for the first touchdown of the game.

videos.headline: Hightower zig-zags for second long TD of game
videos.description: Boise State WR John Hightower follows his 67-yard touchdown reception with a 55-yard touchdown run.
